  "DescIdentified": {
    "type": "cexolocstring",
    "value": {
      "0": "This suit of armor is a magnificent testatment to the skills of craftsmen throughout the realms. Its steel plates are richly patterned and covered in bronze, gold and silver sheets, and no matter where one looks, its surface is polished to a mirror finish.\n\nOn the breastplate's collar, several  magical spells are engraved with the utmost precision. When donning the armor, the wearer quickly feels at ease, almost introspective, as if the gates of a spiritual dam had been opened wide. A profound conneciton to the divine."
    }
